Britain tomorrow at the landmark department store Harrods to 
promote ``Monica's Story,'' her just-published biography. The tour 
will take her from some of London's largest bookstores to quiet 
British towns bracing themselves for the onslaught of attention. 
The book, written by Princess Diana collaborator Andrew Morton, 
chronicles Ms. Lewinsky's affair with President Clinton. 

