therapist, finished No. 1 at the weekend box office, beating the 
teen love-game tale ``Cruel Intentions,'' estimates showed today. 
``Analyze This'' earned $17.7 million in its debut. ``Cruel 
Intentions'' debuted in second place with a solid $13.2 million. 

