	-- Elizabeth Dole: expected to form exploratory committee soon.  
</P>
<P>
	-- Steve Forbes: expected to make official announcement this  
month. 
</P>
<P>
	-- Rep. John Kasich of Ohio: exploratory committee formed, formal  
announcement expected in spring. 
</P>
<P>
	-- Sen. John McCain of Arizona: expected to formally announce  
candidacy this spring. 
</P>
<P>
	-- Former Vice President Dan Quayle: exploratory committee formed  
last month. 
</P>
